com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.optimizers

Class ASTJoinGroupPartition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.optimizers.ASTJoinGroupPartition

  • public class ASTJoinGroupPartition
extends Object
    Partition of a join group, defined by a (possibly empty) list of non-optional non-minus nodes, possibly closed by a single optional or minus node. Each partition maintains a set of variables that are definitely bound *after* evaluating the partition. Note that this list is equivalent to the nodes definitely bound *after* evaluating the non-optional non-minus nodes in the partition (i.e., the OPTIONAL/MINUS will not contribute to this list).
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Michael Schmidt
